at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999979575023, \"rank\": 2.0424819098639178e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she returned a couple years later and this season has run 22 seconds faster than her collegiate best.\\u00c2  Her personal-best time of 3:56.54 was just fifth among entries in her heat, but Bell ran with the leaders from the start and was never in jeopardy of failing to advance.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Times didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t matter in this setting, but Bell crossed the finish line in 4:00.29 seconds, behind only 22-year-old Diribe Welteji of Ethiopia, who ranks No.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diribe_Welteji\", \"score\": 0.9999999998694875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Diribe Welteji\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diribe_Welteji\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diribe_Welteji\"}, {\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999999936590029, \"rank\": 6.338814828178906e-09, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"12 on the all-time and ran 3:59.73.  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIf anyone can take anything from my unconventional route it is that you can get back to something you love, it is never too late,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Bell told Athletics Weekly.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_Weekly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athletics Weekly\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"